\f1\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 
\f0\fs32 Expertise on weighted Automata for WP4.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \'a0\
The Cornell side of the project also has a long experience and deep understanding of weighted automata, their theory, their applications and how they can be learned for various choices of semi-rings of weights. This will guide our study of generalised reward machines and choice of test cases.\
